\Delta E = f(X) +\delta^T \nabla_{\delta}f(X)
f: \Bbb R^n \to \Bbb R
\nabla_X f = \nabla f(X) := \begin{pmatrix}\partial_1 f(X) \\ \vdots \\ \partial_n f(X)\end{pmatrix}
\partial_i f := \dfrac{\partial f}{\partial x_i}
